          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1960-6 台灣教會公報 文類-散文 作者-鄭連坤/Tīⁿ Liân-khun]</span>
          	            	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-9478.htm">請大家關心山地傳道 [ Chhiáⁿ tāi-ke koan-sim san-tē thoân-tō ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12"> Normal   0      0   2      false   false   false                                                         MicrosoftInternetExplorer4   

